Biblically speaking, the witnesses that are there up on stage is there to hold the couple accountable to the vows they are making. 

Ruth 4

Boaz here is brings witnesses for him. The witnesses are there to serve as a blessing. What a great picture for a wedding ceremony! They are not just people that are your friends, but also for people to hold true to your wives.

Malachi 2 ups it by saying that God is your witness. I am the one who is going to hold you accountable. To remain faithful to them.

